text: The Mansion Passos Oliveira was a historic building in the city of São José dos Pinhais, Brazilian state of Paraná. It was built in 1876 and demolished in June 2011. ==References== Category:Buildings and structures in Brazil Category:Paraná State Category:1876 establishments Category:1870s establishments in Brazil Category:2011 disestablishments
title: Mansion Passos Oliveira
